revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yepezes}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yepez'' is the 5411<sup>st</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 6433 individuals. ''Yepez'' is most common among Hispanic/Latino (95.51%) individuals.
